Union ParseResult has value value: i32; error code: u8.

To main, giving i32.
Let result be ParseResult.value with value be 10.
Let total be 0.
Let errors be 0.
Match result:
ParseResult.value with value: total becomes total plus value;
ParseResult.error with code: errors becomes errors plus (code as i32);
otherwise: total becomes total.
Give total plus errors.
